# Embedded Systems Development Environment (Windows)
## Workspace
* Run *setup.bat*
    * Create ***.workspace*** folder under *%USERPROFILE%* directory.
    * Create *devtools* and *projects* folders.
    * Setup basic development tools.
```
+-- .workspace <W:>
|   +-- devtools
|   |   +-- eclipse
|   |   |   +-- app4mc
|   |   |   +-- papyrus
|   |   |   +-- ...
|   |   +-- miniconda
|   |   |   +-- condabin
|   |   |   +-- envs
|   |   |   |   +-- mde
|   |   |   |   +-- ...
|   |   |   +-- ...
|   |   +-- msys
|   |   |   +-- clang64
|   |   |   +-- mingw64
|   |   |   +-- ...
|   |   +-- systemc
|   |   +-- vscode
|   |   +-- ...
|   +-- projects
|   |   +-- ...
```
